title: [Velathae, South Sunrise Road]
description: An old dirt road runs through a gap in the post and rail wooden fence that encircles the town, where it forks to the north, east, and west.  Splotches of sickly plants sprout from the ground in a vain attempt at life, their stems and leaves drooping and slumped.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, south, west
